        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="medium-12 columns" style="padding: 0 50px; 0 50px; margin-bottom: 50px;">
          <h4 class="sub-text">
            Hivelife is a free web application that makes it easy for beekeepers to keep track of their bees and hives.
            Launching on the web in Spring 2015, with mobile applications to follow.
          </h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="medium-12 columns">
